Now, we are collecting
credit.

225
00:16:55,183 --> 00:16:59,241
Your record is gonna have the Friday Prayers
which is a commandment from God.

226
00:16:59,241 --> 00:17:03,095
You go to the Friday Prayer and drop all business.

227
00:17:03,095 --> 00:17:07,110
And God promises
immediately after that, that will make it up to you

228
00:17:07,110 --> 00:17:14,163
money-wise or earning-wise. If you drop all
business and come to the Friday Prayer,

229
00:17:14,163 --> 00:17:19,809
God says He'll provide for you a lot more and much better here in this world.

230
00:17:21,038 --> 00:17:26,581
And by the way, the credits that you accumulate here, they help you here.

231
00:17:26,581 --> 00:17:30,420
You remember last time, I read for you from
Psalms.

232
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:32,648
Psalm 91

233
00:17:32,648 --> 00:17:43,190
where God says He gives word to His angels to carry you, lest you dash your foot against the stone. So, it happens here.

234
00:17:44,120 --> 00:17:49,964
You remember I read for you
from Luke 12:29

235
00:17:49,964 --> 00:17:55,339
that you seek God's kingship over you and
the rest will follow automatically,

236
00:17:55,339 --> 00:17:59,603
and the rest meaning; health, wealth, happiness.

237
00:17:59,603 --> 00:18:03,837
Happiness, you don't know where it's coming from, emanates from your inside.

238
00:18:03,837 --> 00:18:10,068
And you're like an artificially-intoxicated person that is alcohol-intoxicated

239
00:18:10,068 --> 00:18:14,670
cause the real intoxication is God's
intoxication where you are laughing and happy

240
00:18:14,670 --> 00:18:16,344
regardless of what is happening.

241
00:18:16,344 --> 00:18:18,268
The earthquake killed two million people in Tucson

242
00:18:18,268 --> 00:18:20,065
and you are happy and joyous.

243
00:18:20,065 --> 00:18:24,353
So, understanding the events that happen in
the world

244
00:18:24,353 --> 00:18:27,240
and why the earthquakes happen.

245
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:33,276
But the happiness is a internal feeling that
only God controls, nobody else.

246
00:18:33,276 --> 00:18:36,000
And there is false happiness that does not last.

247
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:38,470
And there is real happiness that lasts.

248
00:18:38,470 --> 00:18:42,443
So, you benefit from the credits here in this
world.

249
00:18:42,443 --> 00:18:45,780
And this is a big mistake that most
people out there make.

250
00:18:45,780 --> 00:18:50,650
They think that they have to wait until the
Day of Judgment to cash in their credits.

251
00:18:52,410 --> 00:18:54,561
You start cashing it right now.

252
00:18:54,561 --> 00:19:02,710
So, every morning, we have to ask
ourselves "how many credits do I want?"

253
00:19:03,374 --> 00:19:08,520
The Five daily Prayers are the credits that
you collect daily in your record.

254
00:19:09,217 --> 00:19:13,130
So, we really have to consciously ask "is
our

255
00:19:13,130 --> 00:19:16,330
record going to be empty of credits or full?"

256
00:19:16,330 --> 00:19:21,809
Because that will decide your position for eternity.

257
00:19:21,809 --> 00:19:25,390
Proclaim that it is a great event,

258
00:19:25,390 --> 00:19:30,130
a momentous event that you, the people, are disregarding.

259
00:19:30,130 --> 00:19:32,790
You are totally unaware of it.

260
00:19:32,790 --> 00:19:34,281
Aqem Al-Salat

261
00:19:34,281 --> 00:19:37,843
Allahu Akbar
